  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to prepare the 20th UNFCCC Conference of the Parties in Peru (COP 20)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The 20th UNFCCC Conference of the Parties, COP 20, took place in December 2014 in Lima, Peru. The organization of the COP required not only extensive logistical preparations, but also had to be prepared politically. This included the participation of Peruvian representatives at UNFCCC meetings and other relevant events leading to COP 20. Through the support offered by this project, the short-term financing needs to prepare for the COP 20 were partially covered. The support  also increased the capacity of the Peruvian Ministry of  Environment (MINAM).</narrative>
  </description>
